hifiberry-autorec (0.1.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added configuration file support
  * Defaults can now be saved to ~/.state/autorec/defaults.toml
  * New --save-defaults option to save current settings
  * New --show-saved-defaults option to view saved configuration
  * Saved defaults override built-in defaults
  * Command-line options override both saved and built-in defaults

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 06 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000

